Barwa to Sell Financial District in a ‘Few Days,’ Al-Sharq Says

-- B y   A m i r   I b r a h i m   A l i   S h a b a n a
-- 
2011-03-28T12:08:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/barwa-to-sell-financial-district-in-a-few-days-al-sharq-says.html
Barwa Real Estate Co. (BRES)  plans to sign
a contract to sell the Barwa Financial District development to
state-run  Qatar Petroleum  in the “next few days,” Al-Sharq
newspaper said, citing Ibrahim Fakhro, director of Barwa
investments in Qatar.  Fakhro declined to disclose the value of the sale and said
details would be revealed after the contract is signed,
according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Amir Ibrahim Ali Shabana in Dubai at 
 ashabana@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
